<head>
  <style>
    * {
      background-color: #D8E2DC;
    }

    .navbar div a {
      color: #FFE5D9;
      background-color: #9D8189;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 5px 5px;
    }

    div {
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #9D8189;
    }

    p {
      padding-left: 0.8em;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 3em;
    }

    button {
      background-color: #9D8189;
      color: #FFE5D9;
      margin: 0.7em 0;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .form_section {
      padding-top: 1em;
      padding-left: 0.8em;
    }

  </style>
</head>


<div>
  <h1>Add Some Flavor to Your Ipsum!</h1>

  <h2>with some delicious bacon/bbq words</h2>

  <p>To generate your <b>bacon ipsum</b>, fill out the form below.</p>

  <ul>
    <li>For paragraphs use a number (default is 1)</li>
    <li>For sentences use a number</li>
    <li>ONLY ONE CAN BE USED</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="form_section">
  <form action="/bacon_result">
    <div>
      <label for="num_para">Number of paragraphs: </label>
      <input type="text" id="num_para" name="paragraph" placeholder="1" size="2">
    </div>

    <div>
      <p>OR</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="num_sent">Number of sentences: </label>
      <input type="text" id="num_sent" name="sentence" placeholder="4" size="2">
    </div>

    <div>
      <button><a href="#"></a>Get Your Bacon Ipsum!</a></button>
    </div>

  </form>
</div>
